Shy Guy, Bowser and a Mii driving past the first turn. Shortcuts[edit] Near the big curve there is a ramp where the player needs a Mushroom to cross. Also, after the ramp there is a dirt area with pipes that the player can cross by using a Mushroom. The player can also cut the first turn using three Mushrooms. Glitches[
